CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Ranpak Holdings Corp is a provider of environmentally sustainable, systems-based, product protection solutions for e-Commerce and industrial supply chains. The company offers a full suite of protective packaging systems and paper consumables. Geographically, it derives a majority of revenue from Europe/Asia.
